      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can't shut my brain off at all. im taking like 5mg of melatonin every night but it just isnt doing much. my doctor actually prescribed me some Ambien (zolpidem) to help me get through this rough patch so i can finally sleep. do u think it's okay if i take the melatonin and the Ambien at the same time? just want to make sure i actually pass out so i can function tomorrow.",
