      "content": "thanks for the info. i'm just really worried about being super groggy tomorrow morning tho. if i take them both together, will it actually make it work better? like, would the melatonin help the Ambien hit harder so i don't have to take a full pill of the Ambien? i really want to avoid the morning fog if i can.",
